## Set Wallpaper in Hyprland

# WALLPAPER='/home/legrems/Pictures/wallpapers/wallpaper_3.jpg'
WALLPAPER='/home/legrems/Pictures/wallpapers/PoE - Affliction/BreakerofOaths_2560x1040.png'

